This data connector generates SQL queries to be executed on a SQL database (eg: PostgreSQL or SQL Server) which is behind an HTTP Proxy. It requires HTTP endpoints to be able to process, on a database, raw SQL queries sent by this data connector.
<br><br>
This data connector typical configuration is:
<br><br>
| Parameter  | Default value  | Description  |
|---|---|---|
| host  | `none`  | Hostname of the http endpoint  |
| port  | 443 | Port used to access the HTTP endpoint  |
| ssl   | `true` if port = 443, `false` otherwise  | Whether to use HTTPS or HTTP protocol |
| path  | /data  | Prefix path to access the HTTP endpoint|
| dialect  | `none` | SQL Dialect used to generate SQL queries. Posible values are the one supported by Knex library |
| schema  | `none`  | The schema used in generated SQL queries |
| schemaDescription  | `none`  | The description of the schema. It describes the mapping between data types, properties and relations and the SQL table names and columns  |
| authHeaders  | {} | An object containing the headers to add to HTTP requests to reach the endpoint. Typically used to authenticate the requester. |
<br>
Example of a configuration to reach a SQL Server (MSSQL database) behind the HTTP endpoint `https: //database.olympe.io/data`, that uses an api-key sent in headers to authorise requests:
<br>
```JSON
"data.<data_source_name>": {
    "host": "database.olympe.io",
    "port": 443,
    "ssl": true,
    "path": "/data",
    "dialect": "mssql",
    "schema": "public",
    "#schemaDescription": {
        "dataTypes": [
            {
                "tableName": "Type1",
                "dataTypeTag": "01892a613c82c24881a4",
                "columns": [
                    {
                        "columnName": "property",
                        "propertyTag": "0189dec39e52c645255f"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "tableName": "Type2",
                "dataTypeTag": "0189dec4c5011f7f4a30",
                "columns": [
                    {
                        "columnName": "otherProperty",
                        "propertyTag": "0189dec4e8c4f8ad7599"
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],
        "relations": [
            {
                "tableName": "toTataRel",
                "fromTag": "01892a613c82c24881a4",
                "relationTag": "0189dec5005bb8b4278b",
                "toTag": "0189dec4c5011f7f4a30"
            }
        ]
    },
    "#authHeaders": {
        "apiKey": "1234-abcd-5678"
    }
}
```
